---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: 短记
description: 还没写成文章，但值得先记下来的想法。
permalink: /notes/
---

<header class="inner-hero inner-hero--quiet">
  <span class="inner-kicker">短记</span>
  <h1 class="inner-title">先记下来，再慢慢想。</h1>
  <p class="inner-lede">这里放的是较短的观察和判断。它们不必急着长成文章，也可能在之后被修改。</p>
  <div class="inner-meta">
    <span>{{ collections.notes.length }} 则</span>
  </div>
</header>

<ol class="notes-list" aria-label="短记列表">
  {% for note in collections.notes %}
    <li class="note-row" id="note-{{ note.data.number }}">
      <article>
        <div class="meta">
          <a class="note-anchor" href="#note-{{ note.data.number }}" aria-label="短记 {{ note.data.number }} 的固定链接">#{{ note.data.number }}</a>
          <time datetime="{{ note.date | htmlDate }}">{{ note.date | readableDate }}</time>
        </div>
        <h2>{{ note.data.title }}</h2>
        <p>{{ note.data.description }}</p>
      </article>
    </li>
  {% else %}
    <li class="empty-state">还没有短记。</li>
  {% endfor %}
</ol>
